okay.. it's been a while since i've updated so i thought i'd update. i finally got a day off work for thanksgiving.. my first day off since last week. it was a VERY BAD day at work. then thanksgiving day.. i had to get up and get ready and wait for my mom to come pick me up to go to my grammas for dinner. i was mad about that b/c i missed dinner with my daddy. so then while we're sittin there she was like .. "so i'll be there to get you at about 9 for christmas" so i was kinda confused why she wouldn't be there at noon just like its been for 10 years now. and she said it was christmas eve and i was uber pissed off b/c i told her a week ago that i was NOT leavin on christmas eve. all my life i have had christmas eve and christmas morning with my dad and step-mom and this year shes tryin to ruin it like last year. which everyone knows im not afraid to stand up to anyone specially my mother.. b/c last christmas eve i freakin cussed her out for ruining my christmas and everyone else's.. but anyways.. now i have to go with my mom at like 10pm christmas eve.. b/c i'll be back the next day. ugh... i hate it when my step-mom talks me into stuff.. lol. so then lastnight i found out that im not gettin anything for graduation.. not even a graduation party or anything. also.. the weekend that i get to come back to SA from military school... is when my brother will be graduating. so they are goin to his graduation and i don't get to come home. don't that suck.. so ive been kinda depressed lately just thinkin bout things. the reality of this is hitting me and kickin my butt.

..i really should be gettin to bed really sooon since i have to get up at like 4 tomorrow morning.. but i don't really feel like sleepin right now.. lol.

we did christmas decorations lastnight. so now our trees up and we have a huge grinch too. i told my step mom she shoulda just put a hat on my dad and put him out there.. haha. 

well i get off work at 2 tomorrow so if anyone wants to go hangout then let me know :o)  nighty night kids..

today was SO great! i worked with josh and kevin.. i loved it. i was the only girl and they both are tryin to hook up with me. i wasn't allowed to go to josh's party lastnight =*( . i'd rather go party with horsey anyways. lol. he was tellin evan, and boggs that we're hookin up and then we're gettin married. lmao. josh was like "can i be best man?" lol. this morning when kev was outside, josh was tellin me that i can get anything i want from him.. all i have to do is ask. ():o)  

Yesterday was a kick-ass day too. i was OFF work! I went out with Ashley and Andrew and Ashley's little brother Andrew. it was *fun*. we went to the mall and ate and then we went and messed around in Wal*Mart. lol  of course we went straight to the toys! haha. i got a glow in the dark lugi! he dances and stuff. i couldn't resist the coolness... i HAD to get it. ashley said shes gonna go back and get one too. lol. I got to meet Nick yesterday!! haha. 

Miranda applied at Subway yesterday too. i'mma talk to my boss about it tomorrow and tell him she's cool and he should hire her! :o) hopefully he will!

well kids, my tummy's talkin to me.. its tellin me it wants sum grub.. so i'mma go eat! leave some comments if ya wanna! <33
